<div class="card card--info">
	<p>We need to work out the language and functionality for MARE in the News pages</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
	<h1 class="card__title">{{ story.heading }}</h1>
	{{#if story.imageFeatured}}
	<img class="card__image card__image--no-margin" src="{{ story.imageFeatured }}" alt="{{ story.heading }}">
	{{/if}}
	<div class="card__content">
		<article class="card__text">{{{ story.content }}}</article>
	</div>
	<section class="button-group button-group--space-around">
		<button class="button button--large button--teal" data-url="/mare-in-the-news">Back to All Stories ( do we want a landing page? )</button>
	</section>
</div>
